  section#stacked-list
    h2 The Stacked List
    p.
      The Stacked List Object is usually an unordered list (though it can be ordered) of blocky items.
      These items may be sponsor logos, passes, speakers, and more. This Object is responsive,
      adjusting its items&rsquo; widths at different breakpoints.
